<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please accept this email as confirmation that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">we have applied the discounted premium to your account</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>To confirm, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">our underwriters have agreed to cover the final 2 instalments of your policy</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. This means that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">you don't owe any premiums going forward, but your policy will not expire until DD/MM/YYYY</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please contact us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> if you have any further queries.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind Regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
